The coefficient referred to in Article 3(2)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 493/2006 shall be fixed by Member State as follows:
(a) Belgium: 0,1945;
(b) Spain: 0,0863;
(c) France (mainland): 0,0074;
(d) Ireland: 1,0000;
(e) Italy: 0,4936;
(f) Netherlands: 0,0848;
(g) Portugal: 0,4422;
(h) Sweden: 0,1156;
(i) other Member States: 0,0000.
